// SourceLinkSourceableOnPost returns a predicate.SourceLink
// matching rows whose polymorphic "sourceable" parent is a
// Post satisfying every supplied predicate. Zero predicates
// match every SourceLink pointing at a Post, regardless of
// the parent's columns.
//
// Laravel equivalent:
