// BookmarkPinnablePreloadResult is the typed eager-load
// result returned by (BookmarkQuery).WithPinnable().All(ctx).
// The Bookmarks slice is the same shape
// BookmarkQuery.All(ctx) would have returned; the Pinnable
// map is keyed by Bookmark.ID and holds each row's resolved
